num_sets = int(input())
    for i in range(num_sets):
        today_high, today_low, normal_high, normal_low = input().split()
        today_high = float(today_high)
        today_low = float(today_low)
        normal_high = float(normal_high)
        normal_low = float(normal_low)
        avg_diff = (today_high + today_low) / 2 - (normal_high + normal_low) / 2
        if avg_diff > 0:
            print("{:.1f} DEGREE(S) ABOVE NORMAL".format(avg_diff))
        elif avg_diff < 0:
            print("{:.1f} DEGREE(S) BELOW NORMAL".format(avg_diff))
        else:
            print("{:.1f} DEGREE(S) NORMAL".format(avg_diff))
